{BLOCKER} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature to this creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature or whenever you cast a spell that has "Spark" in its name, your opponent's creatures don't untap at the start of your opponent's next turn.

{GUARDMAN} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature from your other creatures to this creature.) {TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, put up to 4 cards from the top of your deck into your mana zone tapped.
■ At the end of each of your turns, while this card is in the battle zone, you may cast the spell side of this card for no cost.

{MACH FIGHTER} (This creature can attack tapped or untapped creatures on the turn you put it.)
{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ All creatures break an additional shield.

{MACH FIGHTER} (This creature can attack tapped or untapped creatures on the turn you put it.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, put the top card of your deck into your mana zone. Then you may return a card from your mana zone to your hand.
